data.description: Come view this great custom built home with over 3 acres today! This home has been beautifully maintained and updated. Recent updates include a new dishwasher, 2022 roof, updated LED lighting, sealed concrete floors, cleaned gutters,  fresh paint, and more. This home has split bedrooms, custom built in shelves, privacy fence, workshop and a bonus detached garage. The kitchen has a great room view, breakfast bar, a 2nd built in oven, large pantry, granite counters, and large kitchen island. The primary bedroom is spacious with an office, 2 closets, 2 sinks, oversized shower with 2 shower heads and custom cabinetry. Don't forget to ask about the hidden gun storage! Call your favorite REALTOR® today for a private showing!
